curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/13957' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM8049-1/SGM8049-2/SGM8049-4", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM8049-1 (single), SGM8049-2 (dual) and  SGM8049-4 (quad) are micro-power and low voltage  operational amplifiers, which are suitable for battery-  powered systems. These devices can operate from 1.8V  to 5.5V single supply or from ±0.9V to ±2.75V dual power  supplies, and consume only 2.5μA quiescent current per  amplifier. They also provide rail-to-rail input and output  operation.  The SGM8049-1/2/4 provide low power, low bias  current and low noise. These devices fit in small  packages. The combination of the above features  makes them appropriate for various applications.  The SGM8049-1 is available in Green SC70-5,  SOT-23-5 and TDFN-2×2-6L packages. The SGM8049-2  is available in Green SOT-23-8 and SOIC-8 packages.  The SGM8049-4 is available in a Green TSSOP-14  package. They are specified over the extended -40℃ to  +125℃ temperature range.    "}'
